column5: Hey Joey, hope you have a lot of fun today, and don't forget to take lots of pics and post your report tonight  Maureen
Good luck and smile for the camera
Cripes, I'm sitting on hot bricks right now waiting.  Deep Breath, exhale.........  I'll make sure to take pics if they let me.  Joey
you will be great  just have fun with them

Your having a great month Joey !!  1st you get a T-shirt from your secret admirer, then you win a new musky rod, and now your gonna become a TV fish'n star.........nice things happen to nice people  Knock em dead tooday kiddo
Enjoy Joey, and be sure to let us know how it went!
